# Team Page (`/team`)

## Layout
- Title: "Meet the Team"
- Grid layout: responsive (1–2–4)
- Each team member card includes:
  - Name
  - Role
  - Fun fact or short bio
  - Avatar
  - GitHub / LinkedIn links
- Optional: Modal with extended info

## Styling
- Card background: #1E1E1E
- Rounded corners, shadow
- Hover: slight zoom or tooltip
